Package: D3TableFilter
Title: A table widget based on D3.js and Max Guglielmi's "HTML Table Filter Generator"
Version: 0.5
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "Siegmund", email = "thomas.siegmund@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Max", "Guglielmi", role = c("aut", "cph")),
        person("Erik", "Arvidsson", role = c("aut", "cph")),
        person("Mike", "Bostock", role = c("aut", "cph")),
        person("Cynthia", "Brewer", role = c("aut", "cph"))
    )
Description: D3TableFilter provides a powerful and flexible HTML table widget for
    use with the htmlwidgets R library. It allows R users to create HTML tables
    with functions for advanced filtering and sorting. It also allows for advanced
    formatting of table cells using D3 functions.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: 
    htmlwidgets (>= 0.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Enhances: rmarkdown (>= 0.3.3), shiny (>= 0.10.2.1)
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/ThomasSiegmund/D3TableFilter
BugReports: https://github.com/ThomasSiegmund/D3TableFilter/issues
